er\" halign=\"center\" text_align=\"center\" color=\"light\" animation=\"fadeInDown\" bg_img=\"66340\" bg_img_type=\"parallax\" text_fade_out=\"yes\"]\n<h1>Frequently asked Questions</h1>\n[/cg_content_strip][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Expand &amp; Collapse items</h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=\"#e2e2e2\" type=\"small\" position=\"center\" thickness=\"2\" down=\"5\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_toggle title=\"What payment methods do you accept?\" open=\"false\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]We accept the following methods of payment - Mastercard, Visa, Visa Debit and PayPal.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"When will I be charged?\" open=\"false\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]Payment is charged immediately after security checks from your bank issuer and Captiva have been authorized.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"How do I know my order has been placed successfully?\" open=\"false\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]We will send you an acknowledgement email on successful completion of an order on the site. This email will detail the order that you have placed and will give you an order reference number. We would advise you to keep this email safely as you will need your order reference number for any further queries which you may have. Failure to provide us with an order reference number on request will result in a delay with your enquiry. Once your order has been accepted and dispatched to you we will send you a confirmation email.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"I did not receive a confirmation email\" open=\"false\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]Please contact us if you do not receive an acknowledgement email and we will make sure it is not a problem with our system. Acknowledgement emails are generated and sent automatically once an order has been successfully completed. You may need to check your mailbox as it may be treating our emails as spam o